{"tid":1131943,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"食煙人士入一入來","createTime":"2019-04-30T03:29:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T13:04:30.000Z","uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c047b27a5c8b6e088f58aaf0dc09343477fee7e2","tid":1131943,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T03:29:39.000Z","msg":"身邊既人有食有唔食<br />\n唔食個啲人總會叫你戒 話對身體唔好咁<br />\n當然知啦 點會唔知對身體唔好姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但有時做下創作既野 就好想將個mood推出來<br />\n又或者咁講 有時好想Sad下 慨嘆下<br />\n有無人好似我咁撚變態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同埋想問下大家</span></span><br />\n1. 第一次幾時食？（我呀公死左去做啲道教儀式 係咁聽住啲on9音樂 持續三個鐘 頂唔住問我家姐拎左支煙食 當時20-21歲）<br />\n<br />\n2.點解想持續食？（好想保持食煙個mood)<br />\n<br />\n3.邊支煙最難戒？（夜晚收工 聽住歌 一個人返屋企個枝）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前睇過個post<br />\n有個巴打係做地盤<br />\n話最享受係收工一個行返屋企個支煙<br />\n但返到屋企個仔又話「爸爸 好臭呀」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我明呀 你出返來等我地安撫下你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c35b00f22bd04197d4aa6956142b19e3cfcad51","tid":1131943,"uid":122134,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T03:32:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">持續三個鐘 頂唔住問我家姐拎左支煙食</span><br />\n<br />\n點解會覺得食煙可以解決到呢個問題<br />\n即係當一個人正常既認知 <br />\n無人會同你講 食煙係解悶?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw想知啲人點答第一條"},{"pid":"a2db4e20a9620e2ff2d57794e9bb28965e35e0b9","tid":1131943,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c35b00f22bd04197d4aa6956142b19e3cfcad51","tid":1131943,"uid":122134,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T03:32:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">持續三個鐘 頂唔住問我家姐拎左支煙食</span><br />\n<br />\n點解會覺得食煙可以解決到呢個問題<br />\n即係當一個人正常既認知 <br />\n無人會同你講 食煙係解悶?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw想知啲人點答第一條"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T03:34:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都唔撚知呀 可能見到佢地係出面食掛"},{"pid":"22ad37110947035e920f9ce9cf4255153589c530","tid":1131943,"uid":15195,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T03:41:15.000Z","msg":"當自己靜落黎 一個人 百無聊賴 就會食<br />\n一食就會諗好多野 但唯一諗野既時間就係呢三分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最戒唔甩既係飯後煙"},{"pid":"15e8427f6db0160e160b1bab35e7786071f55db5","tid":1131943,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22ad37110947035e920f9ce9cf4255153589c530","tid":1131943,"uid":15195,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T03:41:15.000Z","msg":"當自己靜落黎 一個人 百無聊賴 就會食<br />\n一食就會諗好多野 但唯一諗野既時間就係呢三分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最戒唔甩既係飯後煙"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T03:43:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />前面好撚中<br />\n<br />\n但飯後呢鋪癢我真係無乜<br />\n同fd飯後就會"},{"pid":"827509d2cfdfb654e19d33efd8dcac77b57bdf57","tid":1131943,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15e8427f6db0160e160b1bab35e7786071f55db5","tid":1131943,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22ad37110947035e920f9ce9cf4255153589c530","tid":1131943,"uid":15195,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T03:41:15.000Z","msg":"當自己靜落黎 一個人 百無聊賴 就會食<br />\n一食就會諗好多野 但唯一諗野既時間就係呢三分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最戒唔甩既係飯後煙"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T03:43:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />前面好撚中<br />\n<br />\n但飯後呢鋪癢我真係無乜<br />\n同fd飯後就會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T03:43:23.000Z","msg":"癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ebdcf4caf9ad7af0ad66db93973f47214c17d16","tid":1131943,"uid":20209,"like":0,"dislike":